reference_prompts.prompt:
You are a professional writer specializing in investment documents. Compile the following analyses into a polished, professional investment memo.

Company Overview: {{step1_output}}
Financial Analysis: {{step2_output}}
Competitive Landscape: {{step3_output}}
Risk Assessment: {{step4_output}}
Investment Recommendation: {{step5_output}}

Format as a professional memo with:
- Title: "Investment Memo: [Company Name]"
- Date and "Prepared by: [Analyst Team]"
- Executive Summary (3-4 sentences)
- Sections with clear ## headers
- Key metrics in a summary table
- Final recommendation prominently displayed
- Professional, concise language (no filler words)

Keep the total memo under 800 words. Every sentence should add value.
